{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2208, "height": 3062, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "doc_title", "block_content": "温庄火洼门", "block_bbox": [972, 252, 1366, 332], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "温庄是渑池县北坻坞村的一个组，地处北坻坞东北，与之隔河相望，地名以村中原有温姓人居住而得名。其地自然条件优越，耕地平坦、水源充足、山坡开阔，传说神奇。清初，有温、杜、韩、张、王等多姓相继迁人，惟杜姓丁财两旺，他姓人口渐稀，现今温庄约150人，其中杜姓有百余人。\n", "block_bbox": [326, 408, 2011, 683], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [144, 802, 231, 1576], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "温庄杜姓为杜槐之后，自清乾隆年间迁入温庄。", "block_bbox": [423, 702, 1357, 757], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "温庄世系：", "block_bbox": [427, 780, 645, 831], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "流芳—忠—果—真金—三乐—跃龙芳—槐", "block_bbox": [427, 852, 1650, 907], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "火洼村地处韶山东翼银山寨脚下，南临314国道，是仰韶乡甘涧行政村的一个自然村组，该村自然条件优越，三面环山，中间淤泥坪地肥沃，发展林、牧业得天独厚。该村除农、林、牧业收入外，还利用青石山的资源优势，采挖加工，销往外地，收入可观。自1989年通电，2005年铺上水泥路，1992年起，用二年零七个月，投资30余万元，打深井一眼，水质甘甜，1995年起启用，解决了火洼村自古以来的缺水问题。火洼因缺水原用“窟”，按地势演变为“凹”，后又习惯性变称“洼”。", "block_bbox": [330, 1001, 2015, 1425], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "杜氏自十一世利魁由温庄迁入后，目前火洼村杜姓占总人口的95%，又有20余户杜姓先后迁居南坻坞、坡头、天坛、徐庄、渑池、洛阳、偃师等地。", "block_bbox": [336, 1444, 2016, 1570], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "火洼世系：", "block_bbox": [438, 1588, 656, 1641], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "槐——允炳—廷鳌——利魁", "block_bbox": [437, 1663, 1056, 1714], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "祖茔位于该村西南大坪地，自十一世利魁起茔，至今已二百余年矣，本支不紊，墓冢清晰可辨。现有石碑三座，翠柏葱郁，古柳茂盛，后人可按规祭祖拜谒。", "block_bbox": [338, 1736, 2004, 1863], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "九九", "block_bbox": [161, 2322, 216, 2418], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 12}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9543853402137756, "coordinate": [330.67999267578125, 1001.3869018554688, 2015.369384765625, 1425.514404296875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9523361325263977, "coordinate": [326.82806396484375, 408.14031982421875, 2011.308837890625, 683.4324340820312]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9140358567237854, "coordinate": [338.84912109375, 1736.217529296875, 2004.526123046875, 1863.087158203125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8915078043937683, "coordinate": [336.0478515625, 1444.998779296875, 2016.130126953125, 1570.800537109375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7929466366767883, "coordinate": [423.9422607421875, 702.892333984375, 1357.8131103515625, 757.34814453125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7832207083702087, "coordinate": [437.107421875, 1663.28515625, 1056.50048828125, 1714.957275390625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7242032289505005, "coordinate": [427.27545166015625, 780.3065185546875, 645.7098999023438, 831.5706787109375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7239028811454773, "coordinate": [438.78668212890625, 1588.767578125, 656.1781616210938, 1641.97607421875]}, {"cls_id": 10, "label": "doc_title", "score": 0.6281047463417053, "coordinate": [972.2044677734375, 252.45785522460938, 1366.6605224609375, 332.6799011230469]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6036381125450134, "coordinate": [427.1258544921875, 852.3327026367188, 1650.8704833984375, 907.852