1, 1293], [2010, 1298], [2010, 1355], [341, 1350]], [[340, 1365], [1726, 1371], [1726, 1427], [340, 1422]], [[438, 1441], [2015, 1445], [2015, 1499], [438, 1495]], [[344, 1514], [1675, 1518], [1675, 1571], [344, 1567]], [[442, 1589], [679, 1589], [679, 1645], [442, 1645]], [[440, 1664], [1052, 1664], [1052, 1717], [440, 1717]], [[442, 1737], [2005, 1739], [2005, 1792], [442, 1790]], [[346, 1808], [1843, 1813], [1843, 1867], [346, 1862]], [[153, 2315], [224, 2315], [224, 2423], [153, 2423]], [[1523, 2357], [2074, 2269], [2171, 2869], [1620, 2957]]], "rec_boxes": [[974, 251, 1369, 334], [432, 409, 2009, 462], [338, 480, 2008, 537], [335, 550, 2009, 613], [334, 625, 1195, 688], [430, 703, 1356, 761], [430, 779, 672, 835], [130, 790, 241, 1041], [430, 851, 1653, 911], [438, 1004, 2010, 1054], [348, 1077, 2009, 1128], [138, 1119, 241, 1584], [341, 1147, 2010, 1206], [342, 1218, 2014, 1282], [341, 1293, 2010, 1355], [340, 1365, 1726, 1427], [438, 1441, 2015, 1499], [344, 1514, 1675, 1571], [442, 1589, 679, 1645], [440, 1664, 1052, 1717], [442, 1737, 2005, 1792], [346, 1808, 1843, 1867], [153, 2315, 224, 2423], [1523, 2269, 2171, 2957]]}}, "markdown": {"text": "# 温庄火洼门\n\n温庄是渑池县北坻坞村的一个组，地处北坻坞东北，与之隔河相望，地名以村中原有温姓人居住而得名。其地自然条件优越，耕地平坦、水源充足、山坡开阔，传说神奇。清初，有温、杜、韩、张、王等多姓相继迁人，惟杜姓丁财两旺，他姓人口渐稀，现今温庄约150人，其中杜姓有百余人。\n\n\n\n## 渑池杜氏宗谱\n\n温庄杜姓为杜槐之后，自清乾隆年间迁入温庄。\n\n温庄世系：\n\n流芳—忠—果—真金—三乐—跃龙芳—槐\n\n火洼村地处韶山东翼银山寨脚下，南临314国道，是仰韶乡甘涧行政村的一个自然村组，该村自然条件优越，三面环山，中间淤泥坪地肥沃，发展林、牧业得天独厚。该村除农、林、牧业收入外，还利用青石山的资源优势，采挖加工，销往外地，收入可观。自1989年通电，2005年铺上水泥路，1992年起，用二年零七个月，投资30余万元，打深井一眼，水质甘甜，1995年起启用，解决了火洼村自古以来的缺水问题。火洼因缺水原用“窟”，按地势演变为“凹”，后又习惯性变称“洼”。\n\n杜氏自十一世利魁由温庄迁入后，目前火洼村杜姓占总人口的95%，又有20余户杜姓先后迁居南坻坞、坡头、天坛、徐庄、渑池、洛阳、偃师等地。\n\n火洼世系：\n\n槐——允炳—廷鳌——利魁\n\n祖茔位于该村西南大坪地，自十一世利魁起茔，至今已二百余年矣，本支不紊，墓冢清晰可辨。现有石碑三座，翠柏葱郁，古柳茂盛，后人可按规祭祖拜谒。\n\n九九", "isStart": false, "isEnd": true, "images": {}}, "outputImages": {"layout_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//86f411a4-d38f-45ae-a42c-b265f2f61790/layout_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A48%3A05Z%2F-1%2F%2F3fac1d52f6c11786fc185d7ee252b885bf0ded8a2df15bc2e97a863ff48209d9", "region_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//86f411a4-d38f-45ae-a42c-b265f2f61790/region_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A48%3A06Z%2F-1%2F%2Fad12720c183de87dd6d2267c9995d73654014fabd63e58f2b29b4f8146cc53e3", "overall_ocr_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//86f411a4-d38f-45ae-a42c-b265f2f61790/overall_ocr_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A48%3A06Z%2F-1%2F%2Fc2da76293f262bad3c6092b0d7090c6a94f1d700a8cfdedd60f589ce9cb7daf8", "layout_order_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//86f411a4-d38f-45ae-a42c-b265f2f61790/layout_order_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A48%3A06Z%2F-1%2F%2F43f3938189b42092a872f9d16582d1037946b0607913a5a9146ab425ae2f6a3d"}, "inputImage": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//86f411a4-d38f-45ae-a42c-b265f2f61790/input_img_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A48%3A05Z%2F-1%2F%2Fe036b825ca84042c57fb9c887bbec777f774941a47b1f9651b2db3dfa50a0bf1"}], "dataInfo": {"width": 2208, "height": 3062, "type": "image"}, "ocrResults": [{"prunedResult": {"model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_textline_orientation": true}, "dt_polys": [[[974, 251], [1369, 251], [1369, 334], [974, 334]], [[432, 409], [2009, 409], [2009, 462], [432, 462]], [[338, 482], [2008, 480], [2008, 535], [338, 537]], [[335, 555], [2009, 550], [2009, 608], [335, 613]], [[334, 631], [1195, 625], [1195, 682], [334, 688]], [[430, 707], [1356, 703], [1356, 756], [430, 761]], [[430, 779], [672, 779], [672, 835],